description: The 13th Ukrainian Prime Minister. A woman of many faces. She was recommended by Putin to be one of the Earth representatives in place of Margaret Thatcher because of her health concerns, since Tymoshenko was the strongest woman in Europe in Putin`s mind. Though Putin calls her a Gas Witch and issued a warrant for her arrest, he would have preferred not to have anything to do with her unless the times demand it.
name: Yulia Tymoshenko
